### Health Check
GET https://localhost:5001/api/report/health
Accept: application/json

### Generate Report with Default Query (GET)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/report/generate

### Generate Report with Custom Query (GET)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/report/generate?query=SELECT * FROM inventory WHERE active = true

### Generate Report with Custom Query (POST)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/report/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "SELECT id, name, quantity, price FROM inventory WHERE quantity > 0 ORDER BY name"
}

### Generate Report with Date Filter (POST)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/report/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "SELECT * FROM inventory WHERE created_at >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '30 days'"
}
